1. need cluster 2. to run an application i need deployment 3. for databases need statefulset 4. In inside the data will be store always available in the database means
we need volumes 5. to expose the database and statefulset we need service 6. for suppose deployment is there suddenly got huge traffic need to be increase pods automatically
if traffic is less means need to decrease the no.of pods for that we need HPA to work HPA properly we need to install metric server, configmaps, secrets

