need to give some configurations values means we will need to create configmaps

to need to isolate releted to the whole application is need namespace

for every pod need to be use some contain of cpu, some contain of memory need to provide quality of servive means we will use resource quota

need to be communicate one service to another particular service and no need to communicate another service in such situation for the security perception 
we will use network policies

need ingress to route the traffic and do terminate ssl means we need Ingress
to know the container is healthy or not incase in healthy means it is taking the traffic or not we will use probes 

to monitor the whole application after the deployment we will use prometheus and grafana

